<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Mi dermi ca-ah thawnnak, sifak mi ca, ah rumnak
 Mi zawmi ca-ah damnak, Bawipa nih a, kan tuah piak,
 Mi dermi ca-ah thawnnak, sifak mi ca-ah rumnak
 Mi zawmi ca-ah damnak, Bawipa nih a, kan tuah piak.

[C1]
   Hossana, Hossana
   An thahmi, tuu fa no
   Hossana, Hossana
   Thihnak in, a tho than cang.

[V2]
 Nunnak tiva, ka tan lai, Kan sualnak a, ttawl dih cang
 Vancung in dawt-nak cerhti, Khrih thisen kei, ca a luang,
 Kan sualnak ti-li chungin, Bawipa nih a, kan chuah cang
 Khamhnak hla dawh, ka sa lai, Jesuh nih a, kan luatter.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
<aka>HOSANA</aka>
<title>BAWIPA NIH A KAN TUAH PIAK</title>
</song>